cmd_help() {
  cat <<'EOF'
atomic — atomic commit pipeline CLI

Commands:
  status           Pipeline state derived from spec.md (none/proposed/applying/ready)
  progress         M/N changes complete
  reset            Delete spec.md and clear atomic/ pipeline state
  show-spec        Print current atomic/spec.md
  show-context     Print current atomic/context.md
  commit           Create git commit (refuses if any [ ] items remain in spec.md)
  push             Push current branch to origin
  clean            Remove spec.md (clear active pipeline)

Flags:
  --json           Machine-readable JSON output instead of human-readable
EOF
}
